header.gameNote: AARON'S AMERICAN ATHLETIC CONFERENCE WOMEN'S CHAMPIONSHIP - FINAL

videos.description: UConn's Gabby Williams comes up with a steal and finishes on the other end with a lay-in for the first points of the AAC Championship Game.
videos.headline: Williams' steal-and-score opens game

videos.description: Kia Nurse finds  Crystal Dangerfield in the corner who knocks down a 3-pointer that beats the buzzer to end the 1st quarter.
videos.headline: UConn's Dangerfield sinks triple at the buzzer

videos.description: UConn's Azura Stevens gets rewarded with a layup after she rejects a USF shot.
videos.headline: Stevens' block sets up fast-break score

videos.description: Geno Auriemma says after winning the AAC Championship that his team accomplished its regular-season goal but still has things to improve on.
videos.headline: Auriemma: 'I like where we are heading'
